# DubberCut Mobile (`apps/mobile`)

## Stack
- Expo SDK 57, Expo Router (file-based), React Native 0.86
- Native tabs: `expo-router/unstable-native-tabs` (`NativeTabs.Trigger`)
- State: Zustand stores in `src/stores/modules/`
- Workspace packages: `@dubbercut/*`

## Icons — no emojis
- **Never** use emoji or Unicode glyphs (▦, ＋, 🎬, etc.) for UI icons
- Use **`AppSymbol`** from `@/components/ui/app-symbol` (`expo-symbols` under the hood)
- Tab bar: `NativeTabs.Trigger.Icon` with `sf` + `md` props
- Add new icons to the `SYMBOLS` map in `app-symbol.tsx`, not inline strings

## Theming
- **Light home/account**: `appTheme` (`src/constants/app-theme.ts`), `Screen variant="light"`
- **Dark editor**: `theme` from `@/constants`, `Screen variant="dark"` (default)
- **Auth onboarding**: dark + lime accent via `authTheme`
- Accent: lime `#C8F135`, not blue

## Routing & auth
- `(tabs)/index` = Home (projects), `(tabs)/settings` = Account
- `Stack.Protected guard={canUseApp}` where `canUseApp = mode === 'local' || !!user`
- Local mode: offline projects on device; cloud mode: API sync + AI translation
- Login routes always outside protected stack: `/login`, `/login/email`

## Feature layout
```
src/
  app/           # Expo Router routes only (thin wrappers)
  features/      # screens + feature components
  components/    # shared UI (Screen, Button, AppSymbol)
  stores/        # Zustand
  constants/     # appTheme, authTheme
```

## Native / patches
- `ffmpeg-expo@0.0.2` is pnpm-patched (`patches/ffmpeg-expo@0.0.2.patch`)
- iOS simulator must link `ios-arm64_x86_64-simulator` FFmpeg slice
- Do not add `ffmpeg-expo` to `app.json` plugins

## Checks
- Run `bun run lint` in `apps/mobile` after TS changes
